{"tid":237013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"送一首歌比所有連登神探","createTime":"2017-05-10T06:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T06:15:46.000Z","uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"581efe216fe3c49204cbe704c0d88d56ae8c7db3","tid":237013,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Gf0zCHuEe2Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGf0zCHuEe2Y&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9ac977fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Gf0zCHuEe2Y</a><br />\n<br />\n從眉頭和動作　分辨<br />\n何謂潛藏內心　惡念<br />\n在迷惑裡拆穿　看著誰在瞞騙<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">最終　發現　故事隨著我預計發展</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n虛偽面目無論裝得再好　心中還是有數<br />\n謊話就是無論編得再好　總捉到你的路<br />\n這樣用力逃避一種眼神　其實你已敗露<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不靠著情報　我都可看(得)到</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假若罪行誰狂掩飾也好　心中還是有數<br />\n虛偽面目無論裝得再好　偏偏欠缺深度<br />\n這樣用力逃避一種眼神　其實你已敗露<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不靠著情報　你心虛我知道</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d8e1dfdd6408acf55302a8b6f75a8701ff858e","tid":237013,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:09:34.000Z","msg":"讀心神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3ec0dd604c3e3bcb99a91977333480a678da3a6","tid":237013,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀心神探<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}